  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Assistant Director (Legal Services)",
  "description": "<p>Responsibilities </p><p>·       Working with senior management to develop and implement policies and actions. </p><p>·       Drafting of regulatory instruments such as legislations and subsidiary legislations. </p><p>·       Providing legal advice and interpretation with respect to various legislations, as well as all other laws of Singapore as required in the discharge of its duties and functions. </p><p>·       Drafting, reviewing and providing sound legal advice on a broad range of legal issues. </p><p>·       Drafting, vetting and advising on general corporate and contractual matters including, but not limited to, tender documents, Memorandum of Understanding (MOUs), tenancy agreements and other commercial documents. </p><p>·       Developing and setting in place internal legal processes and guidance for the various PA Divisions and GROs, including setting up a repository of legal advice.  </p><p>·       Advising and managing potentially contentious matters. </p><p>·      Managing and liaising with external lawyers; and  </p><p>·      Undertaking such other tasks/projects as may be assigned from time to time. </p><p><br />Prerequisites of the Candidate </p><p>·       Possess a law degree and be called to the Singapore Bar (or other commonwealth jurisdictions).  </p><p>·       Have at least 4 years post-qualification experience.  </p><p>·       Corporate work experience (especially in contract law) would be an advantage. </p><p>·       Versatile and self-motivated with strong analytical skills. </p><p>·       Able and willing to multi-task and work well under pressure handling a wide range of legal work. </p><p>·       Good communication and interpersonal skills; the ability to write and reason clearly and compellingly is essential.  </p><p>·       Team player who is also able to work independently with minimal supervision.<br /></p><p></p><p>Talents@Work Pte Ltd (21C0501)</p><p>Lee Kit Ying Deanna (Li Jieying) (1655011)</p>",
